  "subject": "Refractor blueprint-script to avoid cyclic dependency. There is a possibility of cyclic dependencies between blueprint-script module and code module. To avoid cyclic dependency blueprint-script implementation should be moved to Core module. This implementation has zero impact on code functionality and code testing.",
